Maintainer: Victoria Chen <victoria.chen@yale.edu>
Description: The dipm R package implements the Depth Importance in Precision Medicine (DIPM) method. The DIPM method is a classification tree that searches for subgroups with especially poor or strong performance in a given treatment group.
